{"tid":2201821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年城邦派昆左幾隻雙非水貨狗學生妹帶槍去中國，算唔算行得好前？","createTime":"2020-09-14T06:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T06:25:08.000Z","uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20813b3f99cd6c2ac6c0ffab3662eb0120a84984","tid":2201821,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"2012年至2015年期間，中出羊子涉及武器彈藥的走私活動。她被指涉嫌在2012年以網名「洋子」，聯同友人周國興透過聊天軟件QQ建立聊天群組，向大陸地區網民出售違禁品仿真槍，[13] 其後周在大陸因「走私武器彈藥罪」被捕判監，「洋子」在判決書中同被列為主要參與者。<br />\n<br />\n[14]中出羊子又涉嫌從2015年起連同社運友人「神仙B」成立「狗天堂」、「大西洋國際」等網店[15][16]向大陸網友販賣仿真槍，並招募水貨客將槍械走私至深圳郵寄。<span class=\"xx-large\">有六名香港女學生因帶槍被中國公安拘捕及羈押。[17]</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後唔覺有人跟進？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n城邦派行得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱城不嬲真手足嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea9149fbe5f69263483e4a82cf87fb765254fe6","tid":2201821,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"人地去左台灣受民進黨保護再日日指點香港後輩應該點走, 仲唔係真港獨？"},{"pid":"35eace67846a40760b7b6917d225cd60fd7403ad","tid":2201821,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ea9149fbe5f69263483e4a82cf87fb765254fe6","tid":2201821,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"人地去左台灣受民進黨保護再日日指點香港後輩應該點走, 仲唔係真港獨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"算唔算台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc1dbda893eb1e37864502eaac5c545b495983a","tid":2201821,"uid":39710,"like